      <title>德国工厂导致私营部门意外陷入低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/german-factories-push-private-sector-into-surprise-contraction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于德国制造业的低迷状况进一步恶化，德国私营部门 7 月份意外萎缩，削弱了人们对今年下半年经济增长回升的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/german-factories-push-private-sector-into-surprise-contraction</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
