      <title>摩根大通称印度需要出售资产以支持支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/india-needs-to-sell-assets-to-support-spending-jpmorgan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位顶级经济学家表示，印度政府需要重启资产货币化计划，以创造税收以外的收入来源，这既可以帮助资助支出，又可以保持财政审慎的轨道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/india-needs-to-sell-assets-to-support-spending-jpmorgan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 07:29:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
