      <title>政策希望消退 中国股市遭遇 1 月以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/chinese-stocks-trim-losses-amid-signs-national-team-in-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市以今年早些时候大跌以来未曾见过的速度下跌，再次引发人们对尽管实施了政策缓冲，但市场仍将再次陷入自由落体式下跌的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/chinese-stocks-trim-losses-amid-signs-national-team-in-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 04:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抗议活动过后，孟加拉国放宽宵禁以维持经济发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bangladesh-factories-banks-stock-market-reopen-as-curfew-eased</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国在上周发生致命抗议活动后放宽了全国宵禁，允许主要的服装出口部门和银行重新开业，政府试图让经济重回正轨，并阻止外汇储备的下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/bangladesh-factories-banks-stock-market-reopen-as-curfew-eased</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:45:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉和 LVMH 业绩令人失望，股市暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司、路易威登集团和德意志银行公布的业绩不佳导致股市暴跌，随着财报季进入高潮，人们开始担心全球商业状况。纳斯达克 100 指数期货早盘下跌近 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 23:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
